{{Actor| | type = Armor | name = Leather armor | class = LeatherArmor | game = Strife | doomednum = 2018 | spawnid = 68 | spawnname = T_GREENARMOR | convid = 130, 126, 129 }}[[Classes]]: [[Classes:Inventory|Inventory]]&rarr;[[Classes:Armor|Armor]]&rarr;[[Classes:BasicArmorPickup|BasicArmorPickup]]&rarr;<u>LeatherArmor</u>
The leather armor in Strife. It uses the same editor and spawn number as Doom's [[Classes:GreenArmor|security armor]], which is why it uses the same identifier as well. In Strife1.wad, the sprite is actually named ARM2A0 and is [[Sprite renaming|renamed at load-time]] by ZDoom.
